Try it now.

1219
02:02:04,820 --> 02:02:05,750
谢谢  长官
Thank you, sir.

1220
02:02:05,990 --> 02:02:07,480
走吧  祝你们好运
Off you go. Good luck.

1221
02:02:12,430 --> 02:02:13,790
这一下可真有用
I'm sure that got it out.

1222
02:02:15,830 --> 02:02:17,930
这就是我说的厉害角色
That's what I call a hell of a man!

1223
02:02:18,170 --> 02:02:20,360
我也喜欢他的狗
Aye, I like his dog too.

1224
02:02:21,410 --> 02:02:23,200
别在那废话了
Don't stand there yapping!

1225
02:02:23,410 --> 02:02:26,170
这可不是海德公园  是战场
This isn't Hyde Park Corner! The war's over there!

1226
02:02:28,850 --> 02:02:29,780
跟上
Come along!

1227
02:02:29,980 --> 02:02:31,250
快
Come on!

1228
02:02:32,190 --> 02:02:35,020
-谢谢  -一切都很顺利
- Thank you. - Everything's going according to plan.

1229
02:02:35,220 --> 02:02:38,520
等待行动命令  米林"蓝色无边帽"
Stand by to move. Millin,"Blue Bonnet."

1230
02:02:49,740 --> 02:02:51,940
搞什么鬼  
