Oh, my friends. What a day! What a day!

1232
02:03:00,220 --> 02:03:02,490
欢迎来到法国  欢迎来到高利维尼苏
Welcome to France. Welcome to Colleville!

1233
02:03:02,730 --> 02:03:04,850
你太好了真是幸会
Most kind of you. Very nice to meet you- -

1234
02:03:05,130 --> 02:03:07,260
看  我一直留着这个
Look at this. I kept it for you all.

1235
02:03:07,430 --> 02:03:10,270
不过恐怕不够大家喝的
But I don't think there will be enough for everyone.

1236
02:03:10,470 --> 02:03:14,570
也许下次吧  我们还另有预约:打仗
Perhaps next time. We have a previous engagement: the war!

1237
02:03:15,610 --> 02:03:17,240
不必浪费香槟了
Mustn't lose that champagne!

1238
02:03:17,610 --> 02:03:20,600
好了  大家集合  米林"蓝色无边帽"
All right, men, fall in! Millin,"Blue Bonnet."

1239
02:03:22,280 --> 02:03:23,620
再见
Goodbye.

1240
02:03:25,260 --> 02:03:28,110
谢谢  小伙子们  谢谢
Thank you, boys! Thank you!

1241
02:03:33,870 --> 02:03:36,630
法兰西万岁  盟军万岁
Long live France! Long live the Allies!

1242
02:03:37,840 --> 02:03:39,140
要我说的话  
If you ask me, Flanagan...

1243
02:03:39,310 --> 02:03:42,760
这海滩上真有不少古怪的家伙
...there's a lot of very peculiar blokes on this beach.

1244
02:03:44,150 --> 02:03:45,670
欢迎
Welcome!

1245
02:03:46,650 --> 02:03:48,280
欢迎大家
Welcome to you all!

1246
02:05:39,960 --> 02:05:43,190
谢谢  亲爱的  这鞋真漂亮
Thank you, dear, they're lovely!

1247
02:05:45,300 --> 02:05:47,960
最好先穿上试试
Better try them on first.

1248
02:05:52,450 --> 02:05:53,900
我是隆美尔
Rommel speaking.

1249
02:05:54,110 --> 02:05:55,550
早
Good morning.

1250
02:05:56,480 --> 02:05:57,850
什么  
What?

1251
02:05:58,490 --> 02:05:59,850
什么
What!

1252
02:06:00,620 --> 02:06:01,920
哪  
Where?

1253
02:06:02,390 --> 02:06:03,420
诺曼底
Normandy!

1254
02:06:04,490 --> 02:06:06,690
他们已经登陆了吗  
Have they a foothold already?

1255
02:06:07,200 --> 02:06:09,860
必须阻止他们
They must be thrown back!

1256
02:06:10,470 --> 02:06:12,560
装甲预备队呢  
What about the panzer reserves?

1257
02:06:13,670 --> 02:06:17,030
冯・龙德施泰特从元首那获取指挥权没有  
Did von Rundstedt obtain their release from the Fuhrer?

1258
02:06:28,490 --> 02:06:33,090
诺曼底  诺曼底
Normandy, Normandy.

1259
02:06:34,170 --> 02:06:35,760
我真是愚蠢
How stupid of me!

1260
02:06:36,470 --> 02:06:37,920
愚蠢
Stupid.

1261
02:06:39,310 --> 02:06:45,870
霍克岬据点  清晨七点十一分

1262
02:06:51,890 --> 02:06:53,290
就是那
There it is.

1263
