北偏东方向北偏东方向圣米尔伊格里斯在这边
North by east, north by east. Sainte- Mere- Eglise is that way.

1342
02:20:42,090 --> 02:20:43,980
有人移动过路标
Somebody turned that sign around.

1343
02:20:44,190 --> 02:20:47,890
队里除了我就没人看一下指南针吗  
Doesn't anybody in this outfit look at a compass besides me?

1344
02:20:48,330 --> 02:20:49,660
嘿  伙计们
Hey, you guys!

1345
02:20:49,900 --> 02:20:53,600
过来  过来
Over here! Over here!

1346
02:20:54,710 --> 02:20:56,770
过来  跑步
Over here, on the double.

1347
02:20:59,450 --> 02:21:01,780
-要把它弄到哪去  -不知道长官　　　
- Where you taking that? - We don't know, sir.

1348
02:21:02,120 --> 02:21:03,840
我们走错了路
We took the wrong road.

1349
02:21:04,750 --> 02:21:06,480
里面有什么  弹药吗  
What do you got in here, ammo?

1350
02:21:06,760 --> 02:21:08,050
是的  长官
Yes, sir.

1351
02:21:08,420 --> 02:21:11,150
-你们是八十二空降师  -不长官是一○一空降师
- You 82nd? - No, sir, 101.

1352
02:21:11,360 --> 02:21:14,020
现在你们归八十二空降师了
Well, you're in the 82nd now.

1353
02:21:15,170 --> 02:21:17,260
-可是长官  -可是什么
- But, sir, we're- - - But what?

1354
02:21:17,500 --> 02:21:18,870
没什么  长官
Nothing, sir.

1355
02:21:19,770 --> 02:21:21,640
好了  出发
All right, move out.

1356
02:21:25,280 --> 02:21:27,540
-把路标拔掉  -是长官　
- Knock that sign down! - Yes, sir.

1357
02:21:33,860 --> 02:21:37,680
-上面有东西移动中校  -卧倒掩蔽　　　　　
- Something's moving up there, colonel. - Hit the dirt! Take cover.

1358
02:21:40,930 --> 02:21:42,890
是A连的西恩中尉  头
Lieutenant Sheen, sir, A Company.

1359
02:21:45,240 --> 02:21:47,540
中校  是我
Colonel, it's me!

1360
02:21:49,980 --> 02:21:52,400
-你从哪来  -圣米尔伊格里斯
- Where did you come from? - Sainte- Mere- Eglise.

1361
02:21:52,680 --> 02:21:55,380
我们控制了主要道路和广场北侧
We hold the main road and north side of the square.

1362
02:21:55,690 --> 02:21:58,750
德军有一个炮兵连在镇子的另一边  
The Germans have a battery on the other side of the town...

1363
02:21:58,920 --> 02:22:01,450
-控制着乡村地区  -兰斯少校呢
- ...and command the countryside. - And Major Lance?

1364
02:22:01,690 --> 02:22:05,390
-埋伏在广场的一幢建筑里  -F连呢　　　　　
- Holed up in a building in the square. - F Company?

1365
02:22:06,200 --> 02:22:09,760
他们飞过了空降地点  降落到了镇中心
They overshot the drop zone and landed in the middle of the town.

1366
02:22:10,000 --> 02:22:11,030
继续说
Go on.

1367
02:22:11,300 --> 02:22:14,140
那是场恶梦  一场屠杀
It was a nightmare, sir. A slaughter.

1368
02:22:14,410 --> 02:22:16,970
在着地之前就被全歼了
They were mowed down before they hit the ground.

1369
02:22:21,350 --> 02:22:24,010
兰斯少校派我来和你联络
Major Lance sent me to try and contact you, sir.

1370
02:22:24,260 --> 02:22:27,820
他想要你批准撤退  然后在镇外重新部署
He wants your permission to pull back and regroup outside of town.

1371
02:22:30,730 --> 02:22:35,430
不该死的我们要拿下圣米尔伊格里斯
No, damn it. We came here to take Sainte- Mere- Eglise.

1372
02:22:35,600 --> 02:22:37,490
要拿下并守住它
We're gonna take it and hold it.

1373
02:22:38,840 --> 02:22:41,300
跟着中尉  弟兄们
Follow the lieutenant, gentlemen.

1374
02:22:52,320 --> 02:22:54,690
-长官  -谢谢
- Sir. - Thank you.

1375
02:22:56,030 --> 02:22:59,890
英  加两军正从"剑海滩""金海滩"和"朱诺海滩"稳步推进
British and Canadians advancing steadily from Sword, Gold, and Juno.

1376
02:23:03,270 --> 02:23:05,140
"奥马哈海滩"有消息吗  
Anything from Omaha?

1377
02:23:05,370 --> 02:23:09,570
只收到了第一条消息  激战  伤亡惨重
Nothing since the first message: heavy fighting, heavy casualties.

1378
02:23:09,780 --> 02:23:11,870
长官
Sir.

1379
02:23:14,320 --> 02:23:15,550
"奥马哈海滩"来的  
Omaha?

1380
02:23:17,420 --> 02:23:18,450
不是
No.

1381
02:23:22,100 --> 02:23:25,920
真搞不懂德军为什么不投入重型装甲部队
I can't understand why Jerry hasn't brought his heavy armor into play.

1382
02:23:26,800 --> 02:23:29,400
除了二十一装甲师  其余装甲师  
All the panzer divisions except the 21st...

1383
02:23:29,670 --> 02:23:32,200
似乎都远在后方
...seem to be sitting it out in the rear.

1384
02:23:32,810 --> 02:23:33,830
长官
Sir.

1385
02:23:37,050 --> 02:23:40,710
"法军突击队从'剑海滩'直驱内陆  
"French commandos driving inland from Sword...

1386
02:23:40,850 --> 02:23:43,280
已到达乌伊斯特勒昂郊外"
...have reached the outskirts of Ouistreham."

1387
02:23:43,920 --> 02:23:45,480
乌伊斯特勒昂
Ouistreham.

1388
02:26:36,350 --> 02:26:38,010
撤退
Fall back!

1389
02:26:40,820 --> 02:26:42,410
掩蔽
Take cover!

1390
02:26:58,170 --> 02:27:02,270
坦克支援  我们需要坦克支援
Tank support! We must have tank support!

1391
02:27:03,580 --> 02:27:09,370
呼叫"巴士底"呼叫"巴士底"我是"温莎"请回答"巴士底"
Hello, Bastille. Hello, Batille. This is Windsor. Come on, Bastille!

1392
02:27:27,450 --> 02:27:28,780
开火
Fire!

1393
02:27:36,290 --> 02:27:38,710
注意
Attention!

1394
02:27:39,130 --> 02:27:40,560
开火
Fire!

1395
02:27:44,300 --> 02:27:48,590
呼叫"巴士底"呼叫"巴士底"我是"温莎"请回答"巴士底"
Hello, Bastille. Hello, Batille. This is Windsor. Come on, Bastille!

1396
02:27:48,840 --> 02:27:50,530
无法取得联络
I can't get them!

1397
02:27:50,880 --> 02:27:53,000
继续试  我们必须有支援
Keep trying! We must have support!

1398
02:27:53,650 --> 02:27:58,000
坚守岗位  我去找辆坦克
Hold your positions. I'm going for a tank!

1399
02:27:59,290 --> 02:28:01,740
尽可能给我们掩护
Give us as much cover as you can!

1400
02:28:22,180 --> 02:28:24,610
桥  右侧
The bridge, right!

1401
02:28:49,850 --> 02:28:51,220
开火
Fire!

1402
02:28:56,290 --> 02:28:57,660
干掉那门大炮
Try for the cannon!

1403
02:29:03,270 --> 02:29:05,730
把伤员弄出去
Get the wounded out of here!

1404
02:29:33,770 --> 02:29:34,800
回去
Go back!

1405
02:29:35,640 --> 02:29:37,010
离开这
Get out of here!

1406
02:29:38,810 --> 02:29:40,770
不  回去
No! Go back!

1407
02:29:56,040 --> 02:29:58,200
你们不能留在这
You can't stay here!

1408
02:29:58,440 --> 02:30:01,200
我是修道院的院长嬷嬷
I am Mother Superior of the convent.

1409
02:30:01,440 --> 02:30:03,900
这些修女都是合格的护士
The Sisters are qualified nurses.

1410
02:30:04,180 --> 02:30:09,380
可是夫人...我是说嬷嬷我们正在打仗
But madame- - I mean, Mother, we're in the middle of a battle!

1411
02:30:10,590 --> 02:30:14,360
失陪  照顾伤员
Excuse me. Take care of the wounded.

1412
02:30:49,910 --> 02:30:50,930
是坦克
It's a tank!

1413
02:30:53,640 --> 02:30:55,080
是基佛
It's Kieffer!

1414
02:31:05,430 --> 02:31:07,480
在另一边
In the other direction!

1415
02:31:18,410 --> 02:31:21,800
清除碎石  快
Clear away the debris! Hurry!

1416
02:31:58,790 --> 02:32:01,180
我们的空军在哪  
But where is the Luftwaffe?!

1417
02:32:01,470 --> 02:32:04,560
-我正在联系  -好的好的快找吧
- I'm trying. - Yeah, yeah, you're trying.

1418
02:32:12,710 --> 02:32:17,410
英军攻下了一个滩头阵地  正向内陆挺进
The British troops have a beachhead here. They are moving inland.

1419
02:32:17,620 --> 02:32:23,510
美军占领了圣米尔伊格里斯并切断了公路
The Americans hold Ste- Mere- Eglise and have cut the highway.

1420
02:32:23,730 --> 02:32:26,850
我们控制着中央地带
We control this center section.

1421
02:32:27,500 --> 02:32:32,730
美军虽已登陆  但他们被我军困住了
The Americans have landed but their attack has bogged down.

1422
02:32:33,370 --> 02:32:36,230
隆美尔说得对
Rommel is right.

1423
02:32:36,510 --> 02:32:39,970
如果我们能将他们困在海滩上  
If we can hold them on the beaches...

1424
02:32:40,210 --> 02:32:42,210
入侵就会落空
...the invasion will collapse.

1425
02:33:17,360 --> 02:33:18,920
医生
Medic!

1426
02:33:19,130 --> 02:33:20,220
这玩意还能用吗  
That thing still work?

1427
02:33:20,570 --> 02:33:22,590
是的  长官  偶尔能用
Yes, sir, now and then.

1428
02:33:22,840 --> 02:33:25,330
-有没有其他滩头的消息  -无法直接联络　　　　　
- Anything from the other beaches? - Not directly.

1429
02:33:25,610 --> 02:33:29,270
有人收到从驱逐舰发出的闪光信号
A while ago the sergeant picked up some flashes from the destroyers.

1430
02:33:30,080 --> 02:33:34,210
第四师已离开"犹他海滩"向内陆挺进
The 4th Division is off Utah Beach and moving inland.

1431
02:33:34,450 --> 02:33:35,820
内陆  
Inland?

1432
02:33:38,220 --> 02:33:41,350
-第一师呢  -他们被困住了长官
- What about the 1st Division? - They're hung up, sir.

1433
02:33:41,590 --> 02:33:42,990
和我们一样
Like we are.

1434
02:33:47,430 --> 02:33:48,800
行动
Move out.

1435
02:33:58,250 --> 02:34:00,710
医生
Medic!

1436
02:34:08,130 --> 02:34:10,490
-你有什么想法  -想法　　
- What do you think? - Think?

1437
02:34:11,400 --> 02:34:14,700
我们现在死伤至少有一千人
We must have close to 1000 casualties up to now.

1438
02:34:14,870 --> 02:34:17,530
要联络船只来接我们吗  
Do you want me to have the ships start picking us up?

1439
02:34:18,340 --> 02:34:20,970
-你认为有这样糟  -我看不出有其他选择
- You think it's that bad? - I don't see what else to do.

1440
02:34:21,180 --> 02:34:23,010
我们无法登上山头
We can't get up this hill.

1441
02:34:23,180 --> 02:34:26,210
如果不能离开海滩  我们会全军覆没
If we don't get off this beach, we won't have any division left.

1442
02:34:26,420 --> 02:34:28,150
什么  
What?

1443
02:34:28,350 --> 02:34:30,150
这是我们的部下  汤姆
These are our men, Tom.

1444
02:34:30,360 --> 02:34:34,420
带他们来难道是为了送死  然后让剩下的人逃跑吗  
You think we brought them in so some die and ask the rest to turn tail?

1445
02:34:34,660 --> 02:34:37,430
见鬼  不  我们要拿下那个山头
Hell, no. We're gonna get up that hill.

1446
02:34:37,670 --> 02:34:40,230
派人去把"轻骑兵"[突击队]给我找来
Find me somebody to speak for the Rangers.

1447
02:34:40,440 --> 02:34:43,200
海滩背面右侧有一条溪谷
Back down the beach on the right there's a gully.

1448
02:34:43,540 --> 02:34:48,470
有一支重兵把守  两侧有机枪驻守
With a heavily defended roadblock and machine gun nests on both sides.

1449
02:34:48,680 --> 02:34:51,770
-如果我们能杀开一条路  -试过三次了　　　　　　
- If we can blow our way through - We've hit it three times.

1450
02:34:52,020 --> 02:34:54,440
-根本无法接近  -三次不算多　
- We didn't get close. - Three times isn't enough.

1451
02:34:54,720 --> 02:34:57,850
我们要再试  能找些工兵来吗  
We're gonna hit it again. Can you find me some engineers?

1452
02:34:58,060 --> 02:34:59,250
到处都是
They're all around you!

1453
02:34:59,490 --> 02:35:01,830
我是指带有可用装备的工兵
I mean engineers with equipment still working.

1454
02:35:03,700 --> 02:35:05,460
不用和船只联络吗  
Then I shouldn't radio the ships?

1455
02:35:05,700 --> 02:35:06,930
不用  该死的
No, damn it!

1456
02:35:07,200 --> 02:35:11,270
我们需要爆破筒  火箭筒  迫击炮  剪钳  
We need bangalore torpedoes, bazookas, mortars, wire cutters...

1457
02:35:11,440 --> 02:35:14,340
和所有还能行动的人  传话下去行吗  
...and every man that can stand. Pass the word, will you?

1458
02:35:15,950 --> 02:35:17,350
好的  诺尔
Okay, Norm.

1459
02:35:33,970 --> 02:35:36,360
大家都给我听着
Now listen to me, all of you.

1460
02:35:37,240 --> 02:35:39,370
你们要打起精神
You guys got to snap out of it.

1461
02:35:39,750 --> 02:35:42,510
我们要离开这向内陆前进
We're getting off of here, and we're going inland.

1462
02:35:42,780 --> 02:35:45,740
武器呢  将军  我的弟兄手无寸铁了
What about weapons, general? My men lost everything.

1463
02:35:45,950 --> 02:35:48,340
他们得有装备才行
They gotta have something to fight with.

1464
02:35:48,560 --> 02:35:50,390
解除死伤人员的武装
Strip the dead and the wounded.

1465
02:35:50,630 --> 02:35:52,620
凡是可用的武器都带上
Pick up anything that'll shoot.

1466
02:35:52,800 --> 02:35:55,490
用不着我说  你们都清楚
I don't have to tell you the score, you all know it.

1467
02:35:55,770 --> 02:35:58,660
只有两种人能留在海滩上
Only two kinds of people are gonna stay on this beach:

1468
02:35:58,870 --> 02:36:02,830
已经死掉的和将会死掉的  都给我起来
Those that are already dead and those that will die. Get off your butts!

1469
02:36:03,040 --> 02:36:05,770
你们是身经百战的二十九师
You guys are the fighting 29th!

1470
02:36:23,340 --> 02:36:25,060
我看过海军的报告
I've looked at the naval reports.

1471
02:36:25,300 --> 02:36:26,400
怎么样  
Yes?

1472
02:36:27,210 --> 02:36:31,340
据驱逐舰传来的报告说"奥马哈海滩"凶多吉少
According to reports from the offshore destroyers, Omaha is a shambles.

1473
02:36:31,810 --> 02:36:34,540
没有迹象...报告原文是
There's no evidence- - To quote the report exactly:

1474
02:36:34,780 --> 02:36:39,070
"海滩上观察不到有任何活动的迹象"
"There is no evidence of any movement that can be observed off the beach."

1475
02:36:41,060 --> 02:36:42,890
我还是再看一遍比较好
I'd better have a look through these.

1476
02:36:46,400 --> 02:36:47,930
艾克对此有何反应  
How is lke taking it?

1477
02:36:48,130 --> 02:36:51,920
和其他人一样  长官  在焦急等待
Like everybody else, sir. Hanging on by his fingernails.

1478
02:36:54,340 --> 02:36:58,070
不  不  我们必须照方案六重新部署
No, no! We must regroup according to Plan Six!

1479
02:37:02,320 --> 02:37:06,210
喂  喂  能听到吗  
Hello? Hello? Can you hear me?

1480
02:37:06,520 --> 02:37:09,910
我是说我们必须照方案六重新部署
I said we must regroup according to Plan Six.

1481
02:37:11,030 --> 02:37:12,760
废话
Nonsense!

1482
02:37:13,030 --> 02:37:16,300
如果装甲师能来还不算太晚
If the panzers arrive, we still have time to use them.

1483
02:37:20,040 --> 02:37:22,070
我们乘车去海岸
We'll drive to the coast!

1484
02:37:22,540 --> 02:37:24,380
要销毁文件吗  
Shall we remove the files?

1485
02:37:24,780 --> 02:37:29,380
这我不在乎  我要马上去前线  去诺曼底
I don't care! I want to get to the front at once, to Normandy!

1486
02:37:29,590 --> 02:37:30,610
是  将军
Yes, general.

1487
02:37:58,060 --> 02:38:00,420
-其他人在哪  -什么　　　
- Where is everybody? - What?

1488
02:38:02,830 --> 02:38:05,030
我说其他人在哪  
I said, where is everybody?

1489
02:38:07,470 --> 02:38:09,430
我听不见
I can't hear you.

1490
02:38:10,670 --> 02:38:12,540
是那口大钟
It's them bells.

1491
02:38:12,780 --> 02:38:15,630
在我耳朵里响了足有十个钟头
I've had them in my ears for 10 hours.

1492
02:38:15,850 --> 02:38:18,840
叮-当叮-当　　
Ding- dong, ding- dong.

1493
02:38:20,690 --> 02:38:22,810
嘿  中士  兰斯少校在哪  
Hey, sergeant, where's Major Lance?

1494
02:38:23,020 --> 02:38:25,480
指挥所转移到了那幢建筑  他在那
We moved the CP to that building. The major's there.

1495
02:38:25,730 --> 02:38:27,590
去找他  中校来了
Get him, the colonel's here.

1496
02:38:29,100 --> 02:38:30,260
什么  
What?

1497
02:38:32,270 --> 02:38:34,260
停下
Hold it!

1498
02:38:44,080 --> 02:38:46,350
中校  见到你太好了
Colonel, am I glad to see you!

1499
02:38:47,520 --> 02:38:50,580
那些尸体  把那些尸体弄下来
Those bodies. Get those bodies down.

1500
02:38:50,860 --> 02:38:53,250
怎么让他们留在上面  取下来
Why are you leaving them up there? Get them down!

1501
02:38:53,530 --> 02:38:55,220
我们一直处在火力之下
But we've been under fire, sir.

1502
02:38:55,530 --> 02:38:57,450
我知道  但我不管
I know you have, but I don't care!

1503
02:38:57,700 --> 02:38:59,900
快取下  取下
Get them down! Down!

1504
02:39:00,270 --> 02:39:04,230
-我不想让弟兄们留在那  -带一队人去办　　　　
- I don't want those boys left there. - Take a detail and cut them down.

1505
02:39:04,540 --> 02:39:06,310
-马上去  -是长官
- At once! - Yes, sir.

1506
02:39:10,550 --> 02:39:15,220
我们的部队和海上的军队之间有接应吗  
Has there been a linkup between our forces and the troops from the sea?

1507
02:39:15,390 --> 02:39:19,620
不知道  少校  我连他们是否已经登陆都不知道
I don't know, major. I don't even know if the landings took place.

1508
02:39:19,860 --> 02:39:24,620
我只知道必须守住这个镇直到接应部队前来
But I am sure we're gonna hold this town until the linkup does come.

1509
02:39:24,900 --> 02:39:29,400
无论是今天  明天  还是要等到地狱冻结
Whenever that is, today, tomorrow, till hell freezes over.

1510
02:39:31,080 --> 02:39:32,940
哪怕只看在他们份上
For their sake, if for no other reason.

1511
02:39:33,150 --> 02:39:35,640
告诉我敌人的位置在哪
Show me the enemy positions.

1512
02:39:35,850 --> 02:39:38,740
是  长官  德国人的据点就在那
Well, sir, the Germans' strong point is right there.

1513
02:39:38,950 --> 02:39:41,790
就在那边的山上  还没有坦克
That's over there on the hill. They've got no tanks yet.

1514
02:39:42,090 --> 02:39:46,090
他们在公路上方布置了重炮  迫击炮和机枪
They've got heavy guns, mortars and machine gun positions at the top of that road.

1515
02:39:46,260 --> 02:39:48,530
你有多少人  
How many men have you got?

1516
02:39:48,700 --> 02:39:49,790
不够
Not enough.

1517
02:39:50,100 --> 02:39:53,920
上尉和威尔逊中尉带A连去增援兰斯少校
Captain and Lieutenant Wilson will take A Company and reinforce Major Lance.

1518
02:39:54,610 --> 02:39:59,340
其他的人跟我们一起向公路前进
The rest of the command will follow us straight up that road.

1519
02:40:00,650 --> 02:40:01,670
祝你好运  少校
Good luck, major.

1520
02:40:01,950 --> 02:40:04,470
好的  A连  离队
All right, A Company, fall out.

1521
02:40:04,720 --> 02:40:06,810
-二等兵  -是长官
- Private. - Yes, sir.

1522
02:40:06,990 --> 02:40:08,180
真是地狱战场
It's a hell of a war.

1523
02:40:08,390 --> 02:40:10,950
我愿意和您并肩作战  中校
It's a privilege to serve with you, colonel.

1524
02:40:11,160 --> 02:40:15,190
但愿我们能完成我们来此的目的
Well, God willing, we'll do what we came here to do.

1525
02:40:15,400 --> 02:40:17,290
准备好了  头
Ready, sir.

1526
02:40:17,640 --> 02:40:19,300
出发
Move out!

1527
02:40:29,520 --> 02:40:33,080
老头肯定是从昨天开始改变的
The old man sure has changed since yesterday.

1528
02:40:39,000 --> 02:40:41,260
也可能是我们改变了  
Or maybe it's just that we've changed...

1529
02:40:42,370 --> 02:40:44,000
从昨天开始
...since yesterday.

1530
02:40:51,750 --> 02:40:54,380
拉瓦特已率突击队抵达大桥
Lovat and his commandos have reached the bridge.

1531
02:40:55,490 --> 02:40:56,920
鲍勃  你在听吗  
Bob, did you hear?

1532
02:40:57,650 --> 02:40:59,180
是的  我在听
Yes, I heard.

1533
02:41:00,660 --> 02:41:05,120
"圣米尔伊格里斯已被八十二空降师占领"
"Sainte-Mere-Eglise captured by units of the 82nd Airborne."

1534
02:41:06,970 --> 02:41:09,800
"一○一空降师正在'犹他海滩'推进"
" 101 Airborne driving on Utah."

1535
02:41:10,040 --> 02:41:12,730
很好  很好
That's good. Good.

1536
02:41:13,180 --> 02:41:18,070
是的  是不错  但如果不能从"奥马哈海滩"脱身就毫无意义  这我们都清楚
Yes, but if we can't get off Omaha it doesn't mean a damn. We know it.

1537
02:41:18,280 --> 02:41:22,980
我们拿下了两处滩头阵地  一处是英军区  一处是"犹他海滩"
We'll have two cut- off beachheads, one in British zone and one at Utah. Yes...

1538
02:41:23,320 --> 02:41:25,480
但是中间是德军
...and the Germans in between.

1539
02:41:40,980 --> 02:41:42,810
你们是工兵吗  
You guys engineers?

1540
02:41:44,250 --> 02:41:45,980
是  长官  第二九九特种工兵营
Yes, sir, 299th.

1541
02:41:46,220 --> 02:41:49,110
指挥官呢  这里由谁负责  
Where are your officers? Who's in charge here?

1542
02:41:49,720 --> 02:41:52,210
我想是由我负责  长官  指挥官都不在
I guess I am, sir. None of our officers made it in.

1543
02:41:52,430 --> 02:41:54,450
装备呢  爆破筒能用吗  
What about your equipment? Those torpedoes work?

1544
02:41:54,730 --> 02:41:56,650
是的  长官  当然能用
Yes, sir, we'll make them work!

1545
02:41:58,030 --> 02:42:00,730
-你叫什么中士  -J・H・弗勒长官
- What's your name, sergeant? - It's Fuller, sir, John H.

1546
02:42:01,000 --> 02:42:04,500
现在起你是弗勒少尉  不管你愿不愿意
You're Lieutenant Fuller from now on, whether you like it or not.

1547
02:42:07,080 --> 02:42:10,610
派人带上爆破筒去溪谷底部
You send some men down to the foot of that gully with those torpedoes.

1548
02:42:10,880 --> 02:42:14,620
-你和其余的人跟我来  -是长官　　　　　　
- You and the rest of the men follow me. - Yes, sir!

1549
02:42:14,890 --> 02:42:18,420
好了  弟兄们  带上装备离开这
All right, men! Let's move that equipment down here.

1550
02:42:24,830 --> 02:42:28,260
-我有支枪长官  -很好小伙子　
- I got a rifle, sir. - Well, good for you, son!

1551
02:42:28,910 --> 02:42:30,400
"轻骑兵"在待命  长官
The Rangers are ready, general.

1552
02:42:30,570 --> 02:42:32,960
好的  少校  叫他们出发
Okay, major, move them out.

1553
02:42:33,140 --> 02:42:35,870
